{
  "id": "adv_bond_suz_01_07",
  "title": "成宮すず7",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は早く寮を出られましたし、余裕を持って学校に\n到着出来そうですわ！　まさに模範的な生徒――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7833.3333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 10.3999998729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "って、なんですのこの人だかりは！\nまさか、私が登校中と知ったファンの方達！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 19.8999998729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふんっ、私の人気もついにここまできましたのね！\n……あら？　あそこにいるのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 30.3333332062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "応援してくれてるんやねぇ、ありがとうございます～\n握手ですか？　もちろん！　ええですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 39.9666665395
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "優！？　で、では、この人だかりは優のファンの方達\nということなんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ぐぬぬ……こんな所で大勢のファンに囲まれるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.5999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 47.5999998729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "羨まし……無防備過ぎましてよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 58.0333332062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "え～！　そんな、会えただけで感動やなんて\n泣かんといて～？　嬉しくてうちまで泣いてまうわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ファンの方、感激のあまり泣いていらっしゃる！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.5333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 67.5333332062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "それに優のあの嬉しそうな顔……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（負けてはいられませんわ！　一刻も早く私の方に）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.3666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 76.3666665395
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "（みなさんの注目を集めませんと！　となれば……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ～～～！！！　手が滑ってカバンが～～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.9333332062,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-02.m4a",
          "delay": 100.00012710000306
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 86.9333332062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "教科書をぜ～～～んぶ落としてしまったのですわ～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 98.6666665395
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "（な、なんてこと……みなさん優に夢中で、ぜんっぜん）\n（私に気付きませんわ……こうなったら！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.6666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 107.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "え～っと、放課後の歌のレッスンのためにも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.5333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 109.5333332062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "喉の調子を整えておかないといけませんわよね～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あー、あー！　んんっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.8666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 124.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "月明かぁぁぁり照らす光！！　君の光ぃぃぃ！！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（……さっきからあそこでドタバタしてはるんは）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.2999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 130.2999998729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "（すずちゃん？　道端で何をそんなにアピールして……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "歌の練習だけではバランスが悪いですわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.63332812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 138.63332812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "お次はダンスですわ！　ワン！　ツー！　スリー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.6333282471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 142.6333282471
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すずちゃーん、おはよう！　そこで何してはんの～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.3333291372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 148.3333291372
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "こっち来て一緒におしゃべりしたらええやん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.299995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "優！？　べ、別に気付いて欲しかった訳じゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.4666624706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 156.4666624706
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_07-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "優のファンのみなさま、ごきげんよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.1666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 165.6333291372
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
